The only Discord api interface libarary written in C

-faster than other languages in most situations (if written properly)
-conforms to C99 standards for simplicity and cross platform compatibility
-small codebase

REQUIREMENTS
-C99 compliant C compiler
-libcurl (creating http api requests)
-libsws (my custom curl implementation for websockets)
-jansson (json library)
-libopus (not needed yet but will be needed for audio support in the future)
-mandoc (for building the documentaion)

BUILDING
just run '$ make release' to build a optimized stripped build

if you wish to build a debug build which is currently the default
option just run '$ make' or '$ make debug'

CONTACT
if you have any questions, comments, concerns email me at cheddar@jiyu.moe
